less - scrollable file viewer
Executable: /bin/less.sh
Alias: less

DESCRIPTION
  Displays a text file in a
  scrollable viewer.

USAGE
  less <filename>

NAVIGATION
  Up / W       - scroll up
  Down / S     - scroll down
  LeftCtrl     - exit viewer

NOTES
  On terminals smaller than the
  file, scrolling is enabled
  automatically. The last line
  shows the filename and a
  scroll hint.

SEE ALSO
  cat - non-scrollable viewer
  man - manual page viewer
